      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·節南山之什·009.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">何人斯.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼何人斯？其心孔艱。胡逝我梁，不入我門？伊誰云從？維暴之云。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What man was that?
His mind is full of dangerous devices.
Why did he approach my dam,
Without entering my gate?
Of whom is he a follower?
I venture to say, -- of Bao.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-009__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
