      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·節南山之什·009.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">何人斯.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>二人從行，誰為此禍？胡逝我梁，不入唁我？始者不如今，云不我可。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Those two follow each other in their goings; --
Which of them wrought me this calamity?
Why came he to my dam,
Without entering to condole with me?
Our former relations were different from the present,
When he will have nothing to do with me.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-009__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
