      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·節南山之什·009.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">何人斯.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼何人斯，胡逝我陳？我聞其聲，不見其身。不愧于人。不畏于天。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What man was it?
Why came he to the path inside my gate?
I heard his voice,
But did not see his person.
He is not ashamed before men;
He does not stand in awe of Heaven.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-009__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
