      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·節南山之什·009.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">何人斯.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼何人斯？其為飄風。胡不自北？胡不自南？胡逝我梁？祇攪我心。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What man was it?
He is like a violent wind.
Why came he not from the north?
Or why not from the south?
Why did he approach my dam,
Doing nothing but perturb my mind?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-009__005__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
